1
00:00:10,010 --> 00:00:12,012
Kontrak Song Hui-na berakhir
tiga bulan lagi.

2
00:00:12,095 --> 00:00:14,347
Tim 1, hubungi dia dan cek lagi.

3
00:00:14,848 --> 00:00:17,100
Ada ide untuk jadwal Selasa yang kosong?

4
00:00:17,183 --> 00:00:20,895
Kami menargetkan genre
yang bertolak belakang dengan kompetitor.

5
00:00:20,979 --> 00:00:24,399
Saat ini, yang memungkinkan
adalah Hwany dan Jingom.

6
00:00:24,482 --> 00:00:26,693
Bagaimana jadwal hari Jumat?

7
00:00:26,776 --> 00:00:30,196
Minggu lalu ada promosi kompetitor.
Tak berpengaruh, 'kan?

8
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:31,865
<i>Dia sedang apa saat rapat begini?</i>

9
00:00:31,948 --> 00:00:34,492
Bu Yun tiba-tiba hiatus…

10
00:00:34,576 --> 00:00:37,787
Kalau penulis tak bisa dikontrol,
cari strategi lain!

11
00:00:38,621 --> 00:00:40,582
Jika lengah, kita akan tergeser!

12
00:00:40,665 --> 00:00:44,085
Ini buat kalian semua. Dengar baik-baik.

13
00:00:51,843 --> 00:00:53,595
- Terima kasih.
- Ya.

14
00:01:05,065 --> 00:01:06,816
Akhirnya datang juga.

15
00:01:09,736 --> 00:01:11,362
- Temani aku, ya.
- Oke.

16
00:01:11,446 --> 00:01:12,655
Cantik, 'kan?

17
00:01:13,156 --> 00:01:14,991
Aku ingin segera melihatnya!

18
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,331
<i>Awalnya, itu hanya…</i>

19
00:01:23,249 --> 00:01:24,834
<i>serangkaian kebetulan.</i>

20
00:01:28,505 --> 00:01:31,216
<i>Ketika aku berpapasan denganmu</i>
<i>di saat tak terduga.</i>

21
00:01:33,593 --> 00:01:34,594
<i>Kebetulan.</i>

22
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:46,731
Berikutnya, Seo Mi-rae. Silakan ambil.

23
00:01:47,232 --> 00:01:49,109
Ambil yang bagus!

24
00:01:49,192 --> 00:01:50,026
Apa, ya?

25
00:01:51,694 --> 00:01:53,113
Astaga!

26
00:01:56,157 --> 00:01:58,159
- Terima kasih.
- Mirip denganmu!

27
00:01:58,243 --> 00:02:00,411
Imut sekali. Sangat mirip denganmu!

28
00:02:01,121 --> 00:02:03,540
<i>Dari semua hadiah, kau mengambil punyaku.</i>

29
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:06,126
<i>Kebetulan.</i>

30
00:02:14,092 --> 00:02:16,052
<i>Setiap hari kita naik lift yang sama.</i>

31
00:02:18,721 --> 00:02:19,681
<i>Kebetulan.</i>

32
00:02:45,957 --> 00:02:46,833
<i>Saat itu aku sadar…</i>

33
00:02:49,377 --> 00:02:51,963
<i>bahwa aku menantikan kebetulan itu.</i>

34
00:02:55,592 --> 00:02:56,634
Tak hilang pakai itu.

35
00:02:59,345 --> 00:03:00,180
Ya.

36
00:03:03,516 --> 00:03:07,020
<i>Ada kalanya aku sedikit serakah.</i>

37
00:03:09,397 --> 00:03:10,732
Klise.

38
00:03:12,108 --> 00:03:14,402
Bukan klise, tapi klasik.

39
00:03:23,077 --> 00:03:24,370
Pesan satu amerikano dingin.

40
00:03:24,454 --> 00:03:26,164
Dan satu late dingin juga.

41
00:03:32,212 --> 00:03:33,755
- Mau beli kopi?
- Ya.

42
00:03:33,838 --> 00:03:35,506
Pesan satu late dingin.

43
00:03:35,590 --> 00:03:37,175
Totalnya 4.500 won.

44
00:03:39,969 --> 00:03:41,346
Terima kasih.

45
00:03:44,307 --> 00:03:47,977
<i>Ada kalanya juga</i>
<i>aku sok tak peduli dan menyerah.</i>

46
00:03:48,061 --> 00:03:49,103
Ini dia!

47
00:03:49,187 --> 00:03:50,021
Cari ini, 'kan?

48
00:04:00,073 --> 00:04:00,949
Sudah lengkap.

49
00:04:04,118 --> 00:04:06,371
<i>Tapi setiap kali aku menyerah, kau</i>…

50
00:04:21,219 --> 00:04:22,595
Kau sungguh datang.

51
00:04:26,683 --> 00:04:28,434
<i>…melangkah melewati batasku.</i>

52
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:57,922
EPISODE 7
ALGORITMA HATI

53
00:05:01,009 --> 00:05:02,302
Hangatnya.

54
00:05:19,444 --> 00:05:20,570
Sedang apa di sini?

55
00:05:25,783 --> 00:05:26,701
<i>Halo?</i>

56
00:05:27,744 --> 00:05:29,412
<i>Halo?</i>

57
00:05:41,132 --> 00:05:42,133
Produser Park…

58
00:05:46,596 --> 00:05:47,513
Kenapa di sini?

59
00:05:48,097 --> 00:05:49,098
Oh, aku…

60
00:05:49,724 --> 00:05:50,558
Aku hanya…

61
00:05:53,978 --> 00:05:58,274
Aku cuma mencari udara segar.
Sekarang aku mau kembali ke hotel.

62
00:06:00,568 --> 00:06:02,403
- Ayo pergi bersama.
- Tak usah.

63
00:06:02,487 --> 00:06:04,030
Aku bisa pergi sendiri.

64
00:06:04,781 --> 00:06:05,615
Kau mabuk.

65
00:06:06,407 --> 00:06:08,284
Padahal aku baik-baik saja…

66
00:06:29,722 --> 00:06:31,099
Barusan itu

67
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:34,435
kau bilang, "Kau sungguh datang."

68
00:06:37,063 --> 00:06:38,189
Apa maksudnya?

69
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:42,026
Sepertinya karena aku sedang mabuk. Maaf.

70
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:43,903
Kaukira aku orang lain?

71
00:06:44,487 --> 00:06:47,073
Tidak, bukan begitu.

72
00:06:48,616 --> 00:06:53,079
Bukankah tadi kau sedang minum
dengan yang lain?

73
00:06:53,579 --> 00:06:54,747
Kenapa kau di sini?

74
00:06:54,831 --> 00:06:55,748
Aku hanya…

75
00:06:57,041 --> 00:06:58,668
Aku ingin cari udara segar.

76
00:07:05,049 --> 00:07:06,300
Hubunganmu berjalan lancar?

77
00:07:12,515 --> 00:07:13,349
Ya.

78
00:07:16,477 --> 00:07:17,562
Baguslah.

79
00:07:37,123 --> 00:07:39,208
Kamarku di sini.

80
00:07:39,792 --> 00:07:40,626
Oke.

81
00:07:42,253 --> 00:07:43,171
Selamat malam.

82
00:07:44,464 --> 00:07:45,339
Sampai jumpa.

83
00:08:16,704 --> 00:08:19,248
<i>Kyeong-nam, kau di mana?</i>
<i>Kenapa tak kembali?</i>

84
00:08:19,332 --> 00:08:21,959
<i>Dong-min benar-benar mabuk sekarang.</i>

85
00:08:22,043 --> 00:08:23,628
<i>Lucu sekali!</i>

86
00:08:23,711 --> 00:08:25,421
<i>Hye-bin lebih mabuk dariku.</i>

87
00:08:25,505 --> 00:08:28,841
<i>Kau kembali ke hotel?</i>
<i>Nanti datang lagi, 'kan?</i>

88
00:08:33,971 --> 00:08:37,892
<i>Aku lelah, jadi ingin tidur.</i>
<i>Nikmatilah waktu kalian.</i>

89
00:09:04,168 --> 00:09:07,171
<i>Seo Mi-rae, kau tidur juga</i>
<i>setelah mengantar Bu Yun?</i>

90
00:09:10,258 --> 00:09:14,303
<i>Ya, sepertinya aku kelelahan.</i>
<i>Bersenang-senanglah!</i>

91
00:09:17,098 --> 00:09:18,516
Dia selalu berbohong.

92
00:09:19,016 --> 00:09:21,686
Bu Yun, aku sudah panggil taksi.

93
00:09:21,769 --> 00:09:24,313
Waktunya kembali ke hotel dan tidur. Oke?

94
00:09:24,397 --> 00:09:26,524
- Berikan lenganmu.
- Lepaskan aku!

95
00:09:27,483 --> 00:09:30,945
Hei, kenapa kau tidak berpacaran?

96
00:09:31,946 --> 00:09:35,366
Dulu kau punya pacar
waktu bekerja denganku.

97
00:09:35,866 --> 00:09:38,369
Setelah putus, kau tak punya pacar lagi?

98
00:09:39,662 --> 00:09:42,248
Kenapa tiba-tiba kau membahas itu?

99
00:09:42,748 --> 00:09:46,627
Selain itu, mana bisa aku pacaran
kalau kau selalu menyusahkanku?

100
00:09:46,711 --> 00:09:49,880
Jika tak ada yang menyukaimu,

101
00:09:49,964 --> 00:09:52,258
setidaknya carilah gebetan.

102
00:09:52,341 --> 00:09:55,553
Itu urusanku. Taksinya datang. Ayo.

103
00:09:55,636 --> 00:09:57,888
Oke, aku pergi!

104
00:09:57,972 --> 00:10:00,683
Aku punya dua kucing. Mereka manis sekali.

105
00:10:00,766 --> 00:10:03,352
Aku mau keluar sebentar.

106
00:10:03,436 --> 00:10:04,270
Apa?

107
00:10:05,313 --> 00:10:06,147
Cepat kembali.

108
00:10:15,489 --> 00:10:19,368
<i>Nomor yang Anda tuju tidak menjawab.</i>
<i>Silakan tinggalkan pesan…</i>

109
00:10:50,983 --> 00:10:52,610
CHOI DONG-MIN

110
00:10:57,782 --> 00:10:58,616
Halo?

111
00:10:58,699 --> 00:11:02,286
Kyeong-nam, kau di mana? Hwany mencarimu.

112
00:11:03,579 --> 00:11:04,789
Aku keluar sebentar dan…

113
00:11:04,872 --> 00:11:05,831
<i>Ayo kemari.</i>

114
00:11:05,915 --> 00:11:08,000
Ayo kemari. Kau di mana?

115
00:11:08,084 --> 00:11:09,418
Hei, Mi-rae di mana?

116
00:11:09,502 --> 00:11:10,336
<i>Apa?</i>

117
00:11:11,337 --> 00:11:13,255
<i>Mi-rae, kau di mana?</i>

118
00:11:13,756 --> 00:11:15,758
Produser Seo tak ada di sana?

119
00:11:15,841 --> 00:11:19,637
<i>Kata Hye-bin dia sudah berangkat</i>
<i>dari hotel, tapi belum datang.</i>

120
00:11:20,137 --> 00:11:21,681
<i>Ke mana lagi dia?</i>

121
00:11:22,598 --> 00:11:23,766
<i>Cepat kemari!</i>

122
00:11:54,714 --> 00:11:56,716
<i>Apa yang sebenarnya aku harapkan?</i>

123
00:12:06,642 --> 00:12:09,437
<i>Tak seharusnya aku senang</i>
<i>dia tak punya pacar.</i>

124
00:12:10,604 --> 00:12:12,189
Hubunganmu berjalan lancar?

125
00:12:15,943 --> 00:12:16,777
Ya.

126
00:12:17,987 --> 00:12:20,239
<i>Dia bohong bilang sudah punya pacar.</i>

127
00:12:21,907 --> 00:12:23,033
Baguslah.

128
00:12:24,243 --> 00:12:25,911
<i>Seharusnya aku tahu artinya.</i>

129
00:12:39,258 --> 00:12:41,010
Sudah waktunya aku merelakan.

130
00:12:54,482 --> 00:12:55,775
Tunggu sebentar.

131
00:12:59,236 --> 00:13:00,070
Bu Yun.

132
00:13:01,155 --> 00:13:02,031
Ayo pergi.

133
00:13:03,282 --> 00:13:04,116
Apa?

134
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,201
Bu Yun!

135
00:13:05,284 --> 00:13:08,287
Setidaknya sarapan dulu.
Kenapa pagi-pagi sekali?

136
00:13:08,370 --> 00:13:10,706
Sarapan? Untuk apa sarapan?

137
00:13:13,709 --> 00:13:15,544
Kemarin kau minum banyak…

138
00:13:15,628 --> 00:13:17,254
Berhenti membahas kemarin!

139
00:13:19,507 --> 00:13:22,051
Kenapa? Memang apa yang terjadi kemarin?

140
00:13:23,886 --> 00:13:25,971
Sudah kuduga. Itu cuma mimpi, 'kan?

141
00:13:27,306 --> 00:13:31,018
Kemarin setelah kau dapat penghargaan,
kita minum-minum dan…

142
00:13:31,936 --> 00:13:33,854
Oh, kau bilang kepada Hwany…

143
00:13:33,938 --> 00:13:35,147
Berhenti!

144
00:13:37,358 --> 00:13:39,527
Astaga, aku harus apa? Ayo jalan.

145
00:13:41,153 --> 00:13:42,071
Oh, iya.

146
00:13:42,571 --> 00:13:45,699
- Kau sudah menelepon pacarmu, 'kan?
- Apa?

147
00:13:46,617 --> 00:13:50,204
Awalnya aku tak percaya,
tapi dia ramah dan suaranya bagus.

148
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:52,623
Kok kau tahu…

149
00:13:52,706 --> 00:13:56,961
Waktu kau tertidur kemarin,
aku menjawab telepon dari pacarmu.

150
00:13:57,044 --> 00:13:58,045
Hei!

151
00:13:58,712 --> 00:14:01,257
- Kenapa kau mengangkatnya?
- Apa?

152
00:14:02,132 --> 00:14:05,261
Ponselmu berdering terus,
jadi mungkin ada yang khawatir…

153
00:14:05,344 --> 00:14:08,347
Kau sungguh mengesalkan!

154
00:14:09,014 --> 00:14:10,307
Bu Yun!

155
00:14:11,642 --> 00:14:13,185
Dia kenapa lagi?

156
00:14:24,196 --> 00:14:25,281
Kyeong-nam!

157
00:14:26,115 --> 00:14:29,410
Aku mau mati rasanya.
Ayo kita makan gukbap.

158
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:31,328
- Mana yang lain?
- Beli kopi.

159
00:14:32,997 --> 00:14:34,248
Hei, di sini. Kopi!

160
00:14:35,541 --> 00:14:37,918
- Produser Park. Kopimu.
- Terima kasih.

161
00:14:38,002 --> 00:14:39,211
Aku kopi hangat.

162
00:14:40,796 --> 00:14:41,797
Mi-rae di mana?

163
00:14:43,799 --> 00:14:45,551
Dia dan Bu Yun pulang duluan.

164
00:14:57,646 --> 00:14:58,814
Mau menghilangkan pengar?

165
00:14:58,898 --> 00:15:00,149
- Setuju.
- Ayo pergi.

166
00:15:00,232 --> 00:15:01,066
Ya.

167
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:04,904
Kak, kenapa kemarin kau pulang duluan?

168
00:15:04,987 --> 00:15:06,447
Kau bau miras.

169
00:15:06,947 --> 00:15:08,324
Ayolah, jangan begitu.

170
00:15:08,407 --> 00:15:09,742
Menjauh dariku.

171
00:15:09,825 --> 00:15:11,702
Kyeong-nam, kenapa kau tak datang?

172
00:15:11,785 --> 00:15:13,495
Seperti baru kenal saja!

173
00:15:23,422 --> 00:15:26,634
Memang benar, rumah adalah tempat terbaik.

174
00:15:39,188 --> 00:15:40,272
DONG-MIN MENGIRIM FOTO

175
00:15:45,361 --> 00:15:47,696
Astaga, kelihatannya seru sekali.

176
00:16:07,633 --> 00:16:09,760
- Halo?
<i>- Kemarin kau pulang dengan aman?</i>

177
00:16:12,304 --> 00:16:13,138
Ya.

178
00:16:14,014 --> 00:16:16,308
<i>Aku tak enak kemarin tak jadi datang.</i>

179
00:16:18,060 --> 00:16:19,269
Tidak apa-apa.

180
00:16:19,353 --> 00:16:21,897
Aku kaget kau tiba-tiba menelepon.

181
00:16:22,398 --> 00:16:24,900
<i>Aku takut tak sanggup pergi</i>
<i>jika melihatmu.</i>

182
00:16:24,984 --> 00:16:26,652
<i>Tampaknya kau tak sedih, ya?</i>

183
00:16:27,736 --> 00:16:29,947
Apa maksudmu? Kau mau pergi?

184
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:31,490
<i>Ayo mengobrol langsung.</i>

185
00:16:32,366 --> 00:16:33,242
Sekarang?

186
00:16:35,285 --> 00:16:36,370
<i>Kutunggu, ya.</i>

187
00:16:55,347 --> 00:16:57,391
<i>Apa ini? Kenapa begini?</i>

188
00:16:57,474 --> 00:16:58,809
Kau datang lebih cepat.

189
00:16:59,309 --> 00:17:00,310
Mau minum?

190
00:17:02,062 --> 00:17:02,896
Tidak.

191
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:04,314
Baiklah kalau begitu.

192
00:17:09,862 --> 00:17:11,363
Kau mau pergi ke mana?

193
00:17:12,781 --> 00:17:14,616
Aku terlalu lama di sini.

194
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:18,370
Ini bukan rencana awalku,
tapi aku bertemu seseorang di sini.

195
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:21,331
Sudah saatnya ke tujuan lain.

196
00:17:23,876 --> 00:17:25,210
Ke mana tujuanmu?

197
00:17:25,294 --> 00:17:28,922
Aku belum tahu.
Ikuti saja ke mana jalan membawaku.

198
00:17:31,008 --> 00:17:33,218
Kalau begitu, kau pergi sendirian?

199
00:17:37,931 --> 00:17:39,308
Kau mau ikut denganku?

200
00:17:41,977 --> 00:17:45,647
Kita bisa pergi bersama,
makan enak, dan menikmati pemandangan.

201
00:17:47,733 --> 00:17:50,027
<i>Apa ini efek dari pekerjaanku?</i>

202
00:17:50,652 --> 00:17:53,655
<i>Begitu mendengar ucapannya,</i>
<i>aku langsung tahu</i>…

203
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:55,991
Aku ingin pergi bersamamu.

204
00:17:59,119 --> 00:18:01,330
<i>…bahwa petualangan bersama Gu Yeong-il</i>

205
00:18:03,248 --> 00:18:05,918
<i>baru dimulai sekarang.</i>

206
00:18:28,816 --> 00:18:30,442
Tunggu sebentar, ya.

207
00:18:30,526 --> 00:18:31,902
- Pasti enak!
- Selamat makan.

208
00:18:32,903 --> 00:18:34,488
Ambil seperti ini. Tunggu.

209
00:18:37,783 --> 00:18:38,617
Bagaimana?

210
00:18:47,251 --> 00:18:48,210
Segar, 'kan?

211
00:19:45,225 --> 00:19:47,394
Ayo ikut denganku.

212
00:19:51,648 --> 00:19:52,733
<i>Sedang apa di sini?</i>

213
00:20:03,118 --> 00:20:04,119
<i>Kenapa di sini?</i>

214
00:20:05,621 --> 00:20:07,539
<i>Kenapa aku seperti ini terus?</i>

215
00:20:09,958 --> 00:20:10,792
Seo Mi-rae.

216
00:20:11,752 --> 00:20:12,753
Produser Seo.

217
00:20:14,338 --> 00:20:15,756
<i>Sekarang…</i>

218
00:20:16,340 --> 00:20:17,174
Ada apa?

219
00:20:17,257 --> 00:20:18,550
Ada apa denganmu?

220
00:20:19,301 --> 00:20:20,719
<i>…aku bersama siapa?</i>

221
00:20:35,108 --> 00:20:36,026
Apa-apaan ini?

222
00:20:36,526 --> 00:20:38,487
<i>Kenapa aku tak bisa membedakan?</i>

223
00:20:39,696 --> 00:20:41,156
<i>Tak seharusnya begini.</i>

224
00:20:46,411 --> 00:20:48,372
<i>Aku sudah sampai rumah.</i>

225
00:20:48,455 --> 00:20:49,957
<i>Sampai jumpa besok.</i>

226
00:21:16,608 --> 00:21:17,442
Halo.

227
00:21:17,526 --> 00:21:18,360
Hai.

228
00:21:25,659 --> 00:21:29,705
Kali ini perusahaan kita
berhasil unjuk gigi. Benar, 'kan?

229
00:21:30,831 --> 00:21:34,668
Tapi dibanding platform besar lain,
kita masih banyak kekurangan.

230
00:21:34,751 --> 00:21:36,086
Kalian tahu, 'kan?

231
00:21:36,169 --> 00:21:39,006
Ayo tingkatkan
kualitas karya dan strategi pasar

232
00:21:39,089 --> 00:21:42,050
agar tahun depan kita menang lagi. Oke?

233
00:21:42,551 --> 00:21:45,178
Sehubungan dengan itu, kemarin aku…

234
00:21:45,262 --> 00:21:48,265
<i>Ya, wajar jika dia menghindar dariku.</i>

235
00:21:48,765 --> 00:21:51,601
- Kita beruntung sekali!
- Kau benar.

236
00:21:51,685 --> 00:21:54,646
Aku kasihan denganmu.
Sekarang pun kau sudah sibuk.

237
00:21:54,730 --> 00:21:55,605
Benar.

238
00:21:55,689 --> 00:21:58,233
Ini kesempatan bagus.
Bisa kukerjakan satu per satu.

239
00:21:58,317 --> 00:22:01,361
Apa kau tak masalah?
Kau pasti sibuk soal promosi.

240
00:22:01,445 --> 00:22:04,281
Memang sibuk. Jadi, tolong bantu aku.

241
00:22:05,032 --> 00:22:05,949
Ya, tentu saja.

242
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,952
<i>Kami bukan satu tim,</i>

243
00:22:09,036 --> 00:22:11,121
<i>wajar jika dia begitu.</i>

244
00:22:11,204 --> 00:22:12,998
<i>Begitulah Park Kyeong-nam.</i>

245
00:22:13,081 --> 00:22:13,915
Oh, benar.

246
00:22:19,171 --> 00:22:22,090
- Ayo kita bahas lagi di sana.
- Oke.

247
00:22:22,174 --> 00:22:23,884
Aku mau minum makgeoli.

248
00:22:23,967 --> 00:22:25,052
Aku tak minum.

249
00:22:25,135 --> 00:22:27,304
Mana bisa begitu?

250
00:22:27,387 --> 00:22:29,222
- Ayo minum bersama.
- Sial!

251
00:22:29,306 --> 00:22:30,307
Kau tidak seru.

252
00:22:32,476 --> 00:22:33,560
Tunggu.

253
00:22:34,394 --> 00:22:36,021
Kenapa aku menghindarinya?

254
00:22:50,285 --> 00:22:53,372
Apa tak bisa besok saja kita makan?
Hari ini dingin.

255
00:22:54,623 --> 00:22:58,251
Aku sampai 30 menit lagi. Tunggu.
Sepertinya aku salah jalan.

256
00:22:58,335 --> 00:23:01,380
Tunggu. Tolong…

257
00:23:02,214 --> 00:23:03,173
Yang benar saja.

258
00:23:03,256 --> 00:23:05,342
Ayolah, beri aku jalan!

259
00:23:08,637 --> 00:23:10,347
Aku tunggu di kafe saja.

260
00:23:13,725 --> 00:23:15,018
Halo, Produser Seo.

261
00:23:15,102 --> 00:23:17,771
Halo. Ada perlu apa ke sini?

262
00:23:17,854 --> 00:23:19,439
Aku ada rapat dengan Kyeong-nam.

263
00:23:23,485 --> 00:23:25,320
Ini late pesananmu.

264
00:23:26,363 --> 00:23:27,322
Sial.

265
00:23:29,741 --> 00:23:32,536
<i>Benar juga. Seperti kata Park Kyeong-nam,</i>

266
00:23:32,619 --> 00:23:35,330
<i>bukan aku yang ditolak,</i>
<i>jadi aku tak perlu begini.</i>

267
00:23:44,756 --> 00:23:46,007
<i>Percaya diri saja.</i>

268
00:23:47,759 --> 00:23:49,094
<i>Busungkan dada.</i>

269
00:23:51,555 --> 00:23:52,764
<i>Senyumlah.</i>

270
00:23:55,100 --> 00:23:57,394
<i>Kenapa? Aku cantik, ya?</i>

271
00:24:05,318 --> 00:24:06,153
HATI-HATI KACA

272
00:24:10,157 --> 00:24:12,451
Kau tak apa? Suaranya keras sekali.

273
00:24:14,578 --> 00:24:15,871
Aku baik-baik saja.

274
00:24:16,455 --> 00:24:18,206
Suaranya saja yang keras.

275
00:24:22,377 --> 00:24:24,337
<i>Ini darurat. Kau di mana?</i>

276
00:24:24,421 --> 00:24:25,881
<i>Kutunggu di luar.</i>

277
00:24:27,716 --> 00:24:30,594
<i>Kenapa? Aku masih 20 menit lagi.</i>

278
00:24:30,677 --> 00:24:33,305
<i>Di luar dingin sekali.</i>
<i>Tunggu di sana saja.</i>

279
00:24:33,388 --> 00:24:34,723
<i>Aku segera tiba.</i>

280
00:24:40,437 --> 00:24:41,354
Kau mau pergi?

281
00:24:42,063 --> 00:24:44,232
Oh, aku cuma mau ke toilet.

282
00:24:48,653 --> 00:24:49,738
Dia tak apa-apa, 'kan?

283
00:24:56,244 --> 00:24:57,204
Apa ini?

284
00:24:58,079 --> 00:24:59,372
Sejak kapan begini?

285
00:25:03,251 --> 00:25:04,794
Bagaimana ini?

286
00:25:12,052 --> 00:25:12,969
Sampai jumpa.

287
00:25:14,054 --> 00:25:15,555
Jangan lupa dioles obat!

288
00:25:20,268 --> 00:25:21,520
Dia linglung sekali.

289
00:25:21,603 --> 00:25:23,772
Bisa-bisa kepalanya terbentur lagi.

290
00:25:23,855 --> 00:25:25,190
Tadi sampai mana?

291
00:25:28,068 --> 00:25:29,027
Tunggu sebentar.

292
00:25:42,958 --> 00:25:43,792
Mirip, ya?

293
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:53,343
Aku minta maaf.

294
00:25:53,426 --> 00:25:57,055
Selama perjalanan, sudah 100 kali
aku menyalakan lampu sen.

295
00:25:57,889 --> 00:25:58,723
Hei!

296
00:25:58,807 --> 00:25:59,933
Itu kenapa?

297
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:01,810
Kau habis berkelahi?

298
00:26:01,893 --> 00:26:03,061
Tidak.

299
00:26:03,603 --> 00:26:06,481
- Hei, ayo pergi. Cepat.
- Oke.

300
00:26:06,565 --> 00:26:08,358
Sial!

301
00:26:08,441 --> 00:26:09,943
Aku malu setengah mati!

302
00:26:10,443 --> 00:26:12,445
Hei, ayo. Cepat kita pergi.

303
00:26:12,529 --> 00:26:13,405
Baiklah.

304
00:26:13,488 --> 00:26:15,115
- Ayo cepat!
- Oke.

305
00:26:20,537 --> 00:26:21,663
Pakai ini.

306
00:26:21,746 --> 00:26:23,290
Terima kasih.

307
00:26:27,294 --> 00:26:29,254
Hei, tertawa saja.

308
00:26:33,008 --> 00:26:34,509
Tunggu…

309
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:37,470
Secepat apa jalanmu
sampai terbentur keras begitu?

310
00:26:37,554 --> 00:26:40,932
Hei. Andai kau tak bawa mobil
dan datang terlambat…

311
00:26:41,850 --> 00:26:42,684
Sudahlah.

312
00:26:43,393 --> 00:26:46,771
Aku cuma ingin perjalananmu nyaman
di cuaca dingin begini.

313
00:26:46,855 --> 00:26:48,189
Dasar kau ini.

314
00:26:49,065 --> 00:26:51,318
Tumben kau lowong. Tak ada kencan buta?

315
00:26:51,401 --> 00:26:52,319
Apa?

316
00:26:55,196 --> 00:26:57,073
Aku sedang istirahat dulu.

317
00:26:58,908 --> 00:26:59,909
Kenapa?

318
00:27:00,535 --> 00:27:02,871
Entah. Aku seperti buang-buang waktu.

319
00:27:05,415 --> 00:27:06,791
Kau mengikutiku, ya?

320
00:27:08,627 --> 00:27:11,421
Bukan begitu. Dari pagi aku sudah dandan

321
00:27:11,504 --> 00:27:14,883
untuk bertemu pria yang tak kusuka
dan berlagak sok manis.

322
00:27:14,966 --> 00:27:17,844
Begitu pulang dan menghapus riasan,
aku seperti tertampar.

323
00:27:17,927 --> 00:27:20,722
"Apa aku menyia-nyiakan masa mudaku?"

324
00:27:21,222 --> 00:27:22,682
Rasanya begitu.

325
00:27:22,766 --> 00:27:25,477
Jangan-jangan ada yang lebih seru
dari pacaran,

326
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:27,520
tapi cuma aku yang tak tahu?

327
00:27:27,604 --> 00:27:30,357
Hei, mulai sekarang, kau harus cari itu.

328
00:27:31,441 --> 00:27:35,487
Tidak. Menurutku tak ada
yang lebih seru dari pacaran.

329
00:27:36,780 --> 00:27:39,282
Masalahnya sulit cari pria yang aku suka!

330
00:27:41,242 --> 00:27:43,495
Sudah tahu jawabannya, kenapa bertanya?

331
00:27:43,995 --> 00:27:46,790
Sudahlah. Pikirkan dahimu harus diapakan.

332
00:27:46,873 --> 00:27:48,333
Besok mau kerja seperti itu?

333
00:27:55,548 --> 00:27:56,633
Sial.

334
00:27:58,134 --> 00:28:00,095
Sempurna. Ini sangat sempurna.

335
00:28:00,595 --> 00:28:02,597
- Tak kelihatan sama sekali.
- Serius?

336
00:28:06,351 --> 00:28:08,978
Begini? Kurasa orang akan sadar.

337
00:28:09,896 --> 00:28:11,022
Atau kupotong saja?

338
00:28:12,232 --> 00:28:15,902
Kau tak tahu? 97% wanita
langsung menyesal setelah potong poni.

339
00:28:15,985 --> 00:28:19,781
Begitu potong poni,
targetmu adalah memanjangkannya lagi.

340
00:28:19,864 --> 00:28:21,991
Kau akan berterima kasih kepadaku.

341
00:28:28,289 --> 00:28:29,624
Kau potong rambut?

342
00:28:29,708 --> 00:28:30,959
Cantik sekali!

343
00:28:31,459 --> 00:28:33,002
- Bagus.
- Terima kasih.

344
00:28:33,086 --> 00:28:34,504
Cocok denganmu.

345
00:28:34,587 --> 00:28:36,339
- Luar biasa!
- Wah!

346
00:28:38,967 --> 00:28:39,801
Apa itu?

347
00:28:40,301 --> 00:28:41,803
Oh, itu wig?

348
00:28:42,637 --> 00:28:43,847
Kelihatan, ya?

349
00:28:43,930 --> 00:28:45,181
Dari dekat kelihatan.

350
00:28:46,516 --> 00:28:48,643
Ada apa? Mau mengubah penampilan?

351
00:28:49,602 --> 00:28:51,020
Apa?

352
00:28:51,813 --> 00:28:53,898
Tidak, bukan begitu.

353
00:28:53,982 --> 00:28:56,568
Hanya mau mengubah suasana hati.

354
00:29:11,082 --> 00:29:12,333
Halo.

355
00:29:18,923 --> 00:29:19,841
Ada apa ini?

356
00:29:21,050 --> 00:29:22,385
Tiba-tiba ganti gaya rambut?

357
00:29:32,771 --> 00:29:34,105
Aduh, malu sekali.

358
00:29:36,983 --> 00:29:37,901
Sudah gila…

359
00:29:37,984 --> 00:29:41,154
<i>Sejujurnya aku tak mau membahas ini</i>…

360
00:29:42,071 --> 00:29:43,865
- Apa?
- Kau belum melupakanku?

361
00:29:43,948 --> 00:29:45,450
Aku sudah gila!

362
00:29:48,453 --> 00:29:49,287
Bu Yun.

363
00:29:49,370 --> 00:29:51,748
- Kau baik-baik saja?
- Apa maksudmu?

364
00:29:51,831 --> 00:29:55,627
Beberapa hari ini,
kau suka tiba-tiba teriak sendiri.

365
00:29:55,710 --> 00:29:57,128
Itu agak aneh.

366
00:29:58,046 --> 00:30:00,632
<i>Kau diam-diam</i>
<i>menaruh camilan di depan ruanganku.</i>

367
00:30:00,715 --> 00:30:02,634
<i>Tunggu sebentar. Soal itu…</i>

368
00:30:02,717 --> 00:30:03,635
<i>- Itu…</i>
<i>- Apa?</i>

369
00:30:04,219 --> 00:30:05,637
Itu untuk So-yeong!

370
00:30:11,267 --> 00:30:13,812
So-yeong, pergilah. Keluar.

371
00:30:13,895 --> 00:30:15,146
Aku penat sekali.

372
00:30:15,230 --> 00:30:16,981
- Pergilah.
- Baik.

373
00:30:22,529 --> 00:30:24,405
Yang benar saja.

374
00:30:29,828 --> 00:30:32,080
Aku berikan sepuluh menit lagi.

375
00:30:45,844 --> 00:30:46,803
Apa?

376
00:30:54,727 --> 00:30:55,937
Dingin sekali.

377
00:30:58,565 --> 00:31:01,025
Ayolah. Aku mohon!

378
00:31:04,863 --> 00:31:05,989
<i>Tunggu 30 menit.</i>

379
00:31:06,072 --> 00:31:07,949
Dia benar-benar…

380
00:31:08,575 --> 00:31:10,243
Selalu minta 30 menit lagi.

381
00:31:18,251 --> 00:31:19,085
Dinginnya.

382
00:31:27,802 --> 00:31:28,761
Astaga…

383
00:31:41,232 --> 00:31:43,276
Aku juga kedinginan.

384
00:31:56,039 --> 00:31:57,749
Penghangatnya cuma satu.

385
00:32:01,002 --> 00:32:02,295
Kau…

386
00:32:04,797 --> 00:32:06,966
Kau juga kedinginan, 'kan?

387
00:32:07,508 --> 00:32:08,801
Kita pakai bersama saja.

388
00:32:21,481 --> 00:32:23,191
Bagaimana dahimu?

389
00:32:24,025 --> 00:32:24,859
Oh, itu…

390
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:27,028
Bengkaknya jauh berkurang.

391
00:32:30,657 --> 00:32:31,532
Syukurlah.

392
00:32:41,125 --> 00:32:44,796
Kak Dong-min bilang
Sabtu kemarin kalian pulang larut.

393
00:32:44,879 --> 00:32:46,714
Pasti seru di sana.

394
00:32:48,466 --> 00:32:49,509
Ya,

395
00:32:50,009 --> 00:32:52,387
kami melihat laut dan makan enak.

396
00:32:54,931 --> 00:32:55,765
Ya,

397
00:32:56,599 --> 00:32:57,433
begitulah.

398
00:32:58,518 --> 00:33:01,688
Aku iri sekali melihat foto kalian.

399
00:33:01,771 --> 00:33:05,775
Aku dan Bu Yun pulang duluan,
jadi cuma makan mi instan di bandara.

400
00:33:08,903 --> 00:33:10,238
Jadi, kau ingin

401
00:33:11,489 --> 00:33:12,782
lebih lama di sana?

402
00:33:23,793 --> 00:33:24,794
Aku…

403
00:33:25,294 --> 00:33:28,673
Ya, tentu aku mau lebih lama di sana
dan makan makanan enak.

404
00:33:29,882 --> 00:33:32,927
Lain waktu, aku ingin main lebih lama.

405
00:33:36,806 --> 00:33:37,765
Begitu, ya.

406
00:33:47,775 --> 00:33:48,609
SELESAI DIUNGGAH

407
00:34:23,853 --> 00:34:25,730
Sampai jumpa besok.

408
00:34:26,522 --> 00:34:27,356
Ya.

409
00:35:04,519 --> 00:35:07,772
AKU INGIN BILANG BAHWA AKU MENYUKAIMU

410
00:36:03,786 --> 00:36:06,789
<i>Aku ingin bilang bahwa aku menyukaimu.</i>

411
00:36:18,050 --> 00:36:19,510
<i>Sudah terima suratku?</i>

412
00:36:21,137 --> 00:36:23,055
<i>Aku malu seperti ini.</i>

413
00:36:23,556 --> 00:36:24,390
Apa ini?

414
00:36:24,473 --> 00:36:25,308
<i>Sebenarnya,</i>

415
00:36:26,767 --> 00:36:28,186
aku agak kesal denganmu.

416
00:36:28,978 --> 00:36:31,898
Kau tak menjawab
saat kuajak pergi bersamaku.

417
00:36:33,232 --> 00:36:35,943
Jadi, awalnya aku ingin melupakanmu saja…

418
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:38,613
tapi ternyata sulit.

419
00:36:40,865 --> 00:36:41,991
<i>Aku merindukanmu.</i>

420
00:37:24,867 --> 00:37:26,661
1: PLANC
2: PRIA UNTUK DIKENAL

421
00:37:30,539 --> 00:37:32,833
<i>Padahal </i>Pria Untuk Dikenal
<i>selalu nomor satu.</i>

422
00:37:32,917 --> 00:37:35,419
<i>- Pasti akan terjun lagi.</i>
<i>- Salam dari tetangga.</i>

423
00:37:35,503 --> 00:37:38,005
<i>- Sudah hebat dia bisa bertahan.</i>
<i>- Hwany bukan main.</i>

424
00:37:38,089 --> 00:37:40,174
<i>Baru kali ini posisinya direbut?</i>

425
00:37:41,467 --> 00:37:44,095
<i>Menang penghargaan dampaknya besar, ya?</i>

426
00:37:44,178 --> 00:37:45,388
Jangan senang dulu.

427
00:37:45,471 --> 00:37:47,974
Tak bisakah kau ikut senang bersamaku?

428
00:37:48,057 --> 00:37:50,142
Kau lihat kejadian di Busan, 'kan?

429
00:37:50,977 --> 00:37:53,187
<i>Besok apa rencanamu? Ayo minum.</i>

430
00:37:53,271 --> 00:37:54,105
Kau tak kerja?

431
00:37:54,188 --> 00:37:57,817
Ini harus dirayakan.
Bisa jadi minggu depan posisiku turun.

432
00:37:59,318 --> 00:38:00,736
Oke, nanti kuhubungi.

433
00:38:14,917 --> 00:38:17,378
- Aku sama sekali tak menduga.
- Benar.

434
00:38:18,421 --> 00:38:19,505
Hei!

435
00:38:19,588 --> 00:38:21,215
- Hai, Mi-rae.
- Hai.

436
00:38:29,223 --> 00:38:30,474
Kau baik-baik saja?

437
00:38:32,101 --> 00:38:33,561
Ya, aku baik-baik saja.

438
00:38:34,061 --> 00:38:36,689
Ini biasa terjadi. Tak usah khawatir.

439
00:38:37,273 --> 00:38:38,107
Tentu.

440
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:40,359
Pasti bisa jadi nomor satu lagi!

441
00:38:40,443 --> 00:38:41,444
Tentu saja.

442
00:38:41,527 --> 00:38:44,822
Meski akan terus bersaing sengit,

443
00:38:44,905 --> 00:38:48,200
tapi pasti bisa
asal penulis bisa jaga mental. Ya, 'kan?

444
00:38:58,127 --> 00:38:59,837
Astaga.

445
00:39:02,631 --> 00:39:05,092
Sudahlah, tidak apa-apa.

446
00:39:05,176 --> 00:39:06,302
Ini wajar terjadi.

447
00:39:06,385 --> 00:39:10,139
<i>PlanC </i>menang penghargaan besar
dan diliput dalam banyak artikel.

448
00:39:14,310 --> 00:39:15,186
Pak Hwang.

449
00:39:15,269 --> 00:39:16,979
Lalu, mau bagaimana?

450
00:39:18,189 --> 00:39:20,566
- Apa?
- Kau pasti punya rencana, 'kan?

451
00:39:21,984 --> 00:39:23,361
Oh, benar!

452
00:39:23,444 --> 00:39:24,570
Aku…

453
00:39:24,653 --> 00:39:28,532
Aku akan bekerja keras
dan melakukan yang terbaik bersama Bu Yun.

454
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:30,659
Hei, Seo Mi-rae.

455
00:39:31,994 --> 00:39:35,247
Kau tahu penjualan koin
<i>Pria Untuk Dikenal </i>seturun apa?

456
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:37,375
- Apa?
- Astaga.

457
00:39:38,250 --> 00:39:40,378
Kontrak Yun Song segera berakhir.

458
00:39:40,461 --> 00:39:43,798
Dalam situasi ini,
kita tak bisa perpanjang kontraknya.

459
00:39:43,881 --> 00:39:46,384
Musim berikutnya akan jadi yang terakhir.

460
00:39:47,176 --> 00:39:50,513
Masih banyak penulis lain.
Mau sampai kapan mengurusnya?

461
00:39:50,596 --> 00:39:52,014
Itu berat sekali.

462
00:39:52,098 --> 00:39:55,434
Aku akan coba bicarakan dengan Bu Yun.

463
00:39:56,018 --> 00:39:59,146
Oke. Bagaimana caranya?
Mau dibicarakan seperti apa?

464
00:39:59,939 --> 00:40:00,773
Ya?

465
00:40:03,359 --> 00:40:04,485
Belum dipikirkan.

466
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:08,489
Hei, ini terjadi juga karena salahmu!

467
00:40:08,572 --> 00:40:13,035
Jika produsernya berjuang mati-matian,
tak mungkin ada karya yang merosot.

468
00:40:13,119 --> 00:40:15,287
Coba lihat kinerjamu ini!

469
00:40:15,371 --> 00:40:17,081
Kau mengurus penulis termahal kita

470
00:40:17,164 --> 00:40:19,375
dan langsung begini dalam beberapa bulan.

471
00:40:19,875 --> 00:40:21,001
Maaf, Pak.

472
00:40:24,839 --> 00:40:25,756
Halo?

473
00:40:33,764 --> 00:40:34,807
Aku tak tahu.

474
00:40:34,890 --> 00:40:37,601
Dia diam saja.
Tak marah-marah seperti biasa.

475
00:40:41,313 --> 00:40:43,023
Besok aku akan ke sana.

476
00:40:43,774 --> 00:40:44,817
Pulang saja.

477
00:40:45,901 --> 00:40:47,736
Apa gunanya kau menghiburku?

478
00:40:48,654 --> 00:40:50,364
Lebih baik kau mengamuk saja.

479
00:40:51,574 --> 00:40:54,076
Aku sudah menduga ini akan terjadi.

480
00:40:55,202 --> 00:40:56,745
Aku sudah merosot.

481
00:40:57,455 --> 00:40:58,873
Cuma itu alasannya.

482
00:41:01,459 --> 00:41:02,543
Bu Yun.

483
00:41:04,879 --> 00:41:06,338
Aku sudah bilang, 'kan?

484
00:41:07,381 --> 00:41:10,885
Aku terkenal cuma karena Choi Si-woo,
bukan karena berbakat.

485
00:41:13,304 --> 00:41:15,222
Sudah waktunya aku merelakan.

486
00:41:16,307 --> 00:41:17,892
Kujual mobilku,

487
00:41:18,684 --> 00:41:19,935
kujual rumahku,

488
00:41:20,769 --> 00:41:22,813
dan kujual… gedungku.

489
00:41:23,814 --> 00:41:26,317
Kenapa berpikir mau menjualnya?

490
00:41:26,817 --> 00:41:29,820
Bu, aku tak akan menyerah
dengan <i>Pria Untuk Dikenal</i>.

491
00:41:30,738 --> 00:41:33,866
Aku akui, fokusku teralihkan
karena masalah pribadi

492
00:41:33,949 --> 00:41:37,703
dan tak berjuang mengerahkan
seluruh kemampuanku. Maaf.

493
00:41:37,786 --> 00:41:39,079
Masalah apa?

494
00:41:40,498 --> 00:41:41,832
Kau malas-malasan, ya?

495
00:41:41,916 --> 00:41:44,460
Tidak, bukan itu…

496
00:41:45,211 --> 00:41:48,506
Intinya, mulai sekarang
aku akan bekerja habis-habisan.

497
00:41:48,589 --> 00:41:51,884
Makanya, kau juga
harus membenahi pikiranmu. Oke?

498
00:41:51,967 --> 00:41:56,639
Apa pun caranya, akan kukembalikan
<i>Pria Untuk Dikenal </i>jadi nomor satu lagi.

499
00:41:57,681 --> 00:41:58,516
Sungguh?

500
00:42:00,142 --> 00:42:03,646
Karena itu, ayo kita makan enak hari ini.

501
00:42:03,729 --> 00:42:04,980
Aku yang traktir!

502
00:42:05,481 --> 00:42:06,440
Kau yang traktir?

503
00:42:06,524 --> 00:42:08,567
Hari ini aku yang traktir.

504
00:42:11,237 --> 00:42:13,614
Jangan dilihat terus. Tak bosan?

505
00:42:13,697 --> 00:42:17,660
Dulu waktu Produser Cho
menyewakan studio untukku dan Bu Yun,

506
00:42:18,244 --> 00:42:21,455
aku di semirubanah
dan Bu Yun di atas. Aku sudah cerita?

507
00:42:21,539 --> 00:42:22,873
Sudah berkali-kali.

508
00:42:22,957 --> 00:42:26,418
Ini adalah momen
yang selalu kuimpikan sejak itu.

509
00:42:26,502 --> 00:42:28,546
Jangan merusak kebahagiaanku.

510
00:42:28,629 --> 00:42:30,256
Oke. Nikmatilah.

511
00:42:31,340 --> 00:42:32,800
Kasihan Produser Seo.

512
00:42:34,677 --> 00:42:36,011
Apa dia sedih?

513
00:42:40,349 --> 00:42:41,475
Dia pasti sedih.

514
00:42:42,643 --> 00:42:45,354
Cuaca dingin begini,
kenapa mengajakku ke sini?

515
00:42:45,437 --> 00:42:47,064
Bagaimana aku pulang nanti?

516
00:42:47,147 --> 00:42:49,275
Kau pasti bosan di daerah itu saja.

517
00:42:49,358 --> 00:42:50,818
Makanan di sini enak.

518
00:42:50,901 --> 00:42:51,944
Tempat apa ini?

519
00:42:52,027 --> 00:42:53,445
Aduh, dingin sekali.

520
00:42:53,529 --> 00:42:56,073
Makanlah semua yang kaumau!

521
00:42:57,741 --> 00:42:58,909
Itu Produser Park?

522
00:43:01,954 --> 00:43:03,539
Sial. Ayo ke tempat lain.

523
00:43:03,622 --> 00:43:05,666
Bu Yun. Halo.

524
00:43:06,458 --> 00:43:09,295
- Halo.
- Hai.

525
00:43:09,795 --> 00:43:11,046
Halo.

526
00:43:11,130 --> 00:43:14,967
Studio Hwany di sekitar sini, ya?
Apa ini pesta perayaan?

527
00:43:15,050 --> 00:43:17,970
Kami sedang rapat saja. Kau sendiri?

528
00:43:18,971 --> 00:43:21,307
Kami hanya ingin menjernihkan pikiran.

529
00:43:23,225 --> 00:43:24,059
Apa kabar, Bu?

530
00:43:24,143 --> 00:43:26,061
- Tentu tidak baik.
- Oke.

531
00:43:26,145 --> 00:43:28,397
Sial. Ayo ke tempat lain.

532
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:29,898
Oke. Kami duluan, ya.

533
00:43:29,982 --> 00:43:31,191
Bocah tengik.

534
00:43:31,275 --> 00:43:33,402
Seharusnya kita yang pergi duluan.

535
00:43:34,862 --> 00:43:35,988
Bu Yun!

536
00:43:51,754 --> 00:43:53,464
Maaf aku terlambat.

537
00:43:53,547 --> 00:43:56,008
- Kami mau pindah tempat.
- Apa? Ke mana?

538
00:43:56,091 --> 00:43:57,718
- Ayo pergi.
- Tunggu!

539
00:44:01,805 --> 00:44:02,765
Tunggu sebentar.

540
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:14,151
- Biar aku…
- Tidak, aku saja.

541
00:44:17,321 --> 00:44:18,155
Silakan.

542
00:44:19,198 --> 00:44:21,367
- Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

543
00:44:21,450 --> 00:44:24,078
Ada apa dengan bocah itu?

544
00:44:25,954 --> 00:44:28,290
Tak usah dilepas. Kita akan pergi.

545
00:44:28,374 --> 00:44:29,625
Aku malas melihatnya.

546
00:44:29,708 --> 00:44:31,418
Oh, begitu?

547
00:44:32,628 --> 00:44:34,129
Aku permisi ke toilet.

548
00:44:34,213 --> 00:44:35,130
Ya.

549
00:44:39,051 --> 00:44:40,636
Bu Yun.

550
00:44:40,719 --> 00:44:43,722
Bisa tak merusak suasana?
So-yeong jadi sungkan.

551
00:44:43,806 --> 00:44:46,684
Jangan menantangku.
Nanti kuajak So-yeong pergi.

552
00:44:46,767 --> 00:44:49,812
Kau culas sekali.
Tak seharusnya kau begitu.

553
00:44:49,895 --> 00:44:52,022
Kenapa tidak boleh?

554
00:44:52,106 --> 00:44:55,025
Apa imbalan kalau kami tak pergi?
Kau mau hiatus?

555
00:44:56,318 --> 00:44:57,736
- Hiatus?
- Ya.

556
00:44:59,988 --> 00:45:01,532
Tentu saja. Aku akan…

557
00:45:03,826 --> 00:45:05,285
- Hei.
- Kenapa?

558
00:45:05,369 --> 00:45:08,831
Kau kaku sekali.
Ini negosiasi antara para penulis.

559
00:45:10,374 --> 00:45:11,208
Bu Yun.

560
00:45:11,709 --> 00:45:14,670
Akan kulakukan apa pun.
Jangan ajak So-yeong pergi.

561
00:45:14,753 --> 00:45:16,630
- Ayolah.
- Produser Seo, dengar?

562
00:45:17,798 --> 00:45:19,049
Sudahlah, Bu.

563
00:45:19,133 --> 00:45:21,635
Sudah apanya?
Katamu mau melakukan apa pun.

564
00:45:23,971 --> 00:45:25,222
Bu, kapan kita pergi?

565
00:45:25,305 --> 00:45:26,849
Apa? Tak jadi pergi.

566
00:45:27,683 --> 00:45:28,684
Apa?

567
00:45:28,767 --> 00:45:30,853
Makanannya enak. Makan yang banyak.

568
00:45:30,936 --> 00:45:33,564
- Pasti panas. Lepas saja mantelmu.
- Benar.

569
00:45:34,523 --> 00:45:35,357
Mau bersulang?

570
00:45:35,441 --> 00:45:36,984
- Ya!
- Baiklah.

571
00:45:38,068 --> 00:45:39,027
Ini enak.

572
00:45:39,111 --> 00:45:41,071
- Bersulang!
- Bersulang!

573
00:45:41,155 --> 00:45:42,698
Ya ampun.

574
00:45:50,080 --> 00:45:52,750
Ini dia. Ayo minum yang banyak.

575
00:45:53,250 --> 00:45:54,918
Ya, ayo minum.

576
00:45:55,419 --> 00:45:56,545
- Ayo!
- Ayo!

577
00:46:01,258 --> 00:46:02,760
Pagi-pagi aku minum susu…

578
00:46:03,260 --> 00:46:04,428
Susu!

579
00:46:04,511 --> 00:46:05,345
Dia minum susu.

580
00:46:06,722 --> 00:46:07,556
Serius?

581
00:46:08,515 --> 00:46:10,434
<i>Saat menyukai seseorang…</i>

582
00:46:10,517 --> 00:46:14,062
Ayo masuk ke markas musuh!

583
00:46:14,146 --> 00:46:15,355
Ini tempatnya.

584
00:46:18,066 --> 00:46:20,194
<i>…segala alasan akan dibuat-buat…</i>

585
00:46:23,572 --> 00:46:24,573
Halo?

586
00:46:25,157 --> 00:46:28,118
Mau kupinjamkan?
Tak perlu buru-buru dikembalikan.

587
00:46:28,619 --> 00:46:30,829
- Oh, kalau boleh…
- Ya.

588
00:46:30,913 --> 00:46:33,290
<i>…untuk bisa bersama meski sebentar.</i>

589
00:46:33,373 --> 00:46:34,208
Kalau begitu,

590
00:46:34,917 --> 00:46:37,044
rencanamu saat Natal…

591
00:46:38,545 --> 00:46:39,546
Natal…

592
00:46:43,884 --> 00:46:45,719
Apa rencanamu saat Natal nanti?

593
00:46:45,803 --> 00:46:48,931
Mungkin aku cuma menonton kartun
atau film di rumah.

594
00:46:49,014 --> 00:46:50,140
Kalau begitu…

595
00:46:50,224 --> 00:46:51,600
Astaga. Zaman sekarang,

596
00:46:51,683 --> 00:46:54,853
kehidupan anak-anak muda
lebih membosankan.

597
00:46:54,937 --> 00:46:57,523
Memangnya seberapa seru hidupmu?

598
00:46:57,606 --> 00:46:59,191
Ada rencana akhir tahun?

599
00:46:59,274 --> 00:47:01,985
Waktu itu kubilang bahwa aku punya pacar.

600
00:47:02,069 --> 00:47:03,737
Aku sudah bilang, 'kan?

601
00:47:03,821 --> 00:47:05,447
Benar. Kau bilang begitu.

602
00:47:05,531 --> 00:47:06,824
Kau tak percaya, ya?

603
00:47:07,324 --> 00:47:09,743
Produser Seo bicara
dengan pacarku di telepon.

604
00:47:09,827 --> 00:47:11,620
- Benar, 'kan?
- Ya.

605
00:47:12,538 --> 00:47:13,372
Serius?

606
00:47:14,122 --> 00:47:14,957
Ya.

607
00:47:15,499 --> 00:47:17,209
Dia sangat menyayangi Bu Yun.

608
00:47:18,877 --> 00:47:22,631
Bu Yun, kapan kalian bertemu?
Kau selalu sibuk bekerja.

609
00:47:22,714 --> 00:47:23,715
Apa?

610
00:47:24,716 --> 00:47:25,759
Soal itu…

611
00:47:26,260 --> 00:47:28,971
Aku berusaha meluangkan waktu
untuk bertemu.

612
00:47:29,555 --> 00:47:33,350
Intinya, apakah cuma aku
yang sudah punya pacar di sini?

613
00:47:34,059 --> 00:47:35,811
Ada apa dengan kalian semua?

614
00:47:35,894 --> 00:47:37,396
Ini masa emas kalian.

615
00:47:37,479 --> 00:47:38,772
Mengesalkan.

616
00:47:39,731 --> 00:47:41,358
Ya, aku iri denganmu.

617
00:47:41,859 --> 00:47:44,570
Lebih baik aku makan camilan saja.

618
00:47:48,365 --> 00:47:50,242
<i>Sial. Aku lupa.</i>

619
00:47:51,952 --> 00:47:53,495
Camilannya habis.

620
00:47:55,747 --> 00:47:57,708
Mirasnya juga habis.

621
00:47:58,458 --> 00:48:00,002
Pergilah beli miras.

622
00:48:20,188 --> 00:48:21,982
Aku…

623
00:48:24,693 --> 00:48:26,486
Maaf aku telah berbohong.

624
00:48:28,405 --> 00:48:29,615
Bohong apa?

625
00:48:31,283 --> 00:48:32,117
Aku bilang

626
00:48:33,035 --> 00:48:36,246
bahwa aku sudah punya pacar kepadamu.

627
00:48:39,917 --> 00:48:42,502
Aku tidak bermaksud menipumu.

628
00:48:43,003 --> 00:48:47,257
Aku panik karena sebelumnya
tak pernah ada di situasi seperti itu.

629
00:48:51,386 --> 00:48:52,346
Aku juga minta maaf.

630
00:48:54,598 --> 00:48:55,432
Apa?

631
00:48:56,725 --> 00:49:00,437
Wajar kau merasa tak nyaman
karena pernyataanku yang tiba-tiba.

632
00:49:01,313 --> 00:49:02,606
Aku cuma memikirkan diriku.

633
00:49:09,363 --> 00:49:11,365
Terima kasih sudah bilang begitu.

634
00:49:12,616 --> 00:49:15,619
Sejujurnya, belakangan ini
itu sedikit mengusikku.

635
00:49:16,411 --> 00:49:17,245
Aku…

636
00:49:17,996 --> 00:49:21,625
Aku terus teringat kau bilang sedih
sebelum kita ke Busan.

637
00:49:24,211 --> 00:49:25,504
Aku tidak sedih lagi.

638
00:49:29,299 --> 00:49:30,300
Benarkah?

639
00:49:32,594 --> 00:49:33,720
Syukurlah.

640
00:49:39,643 --> 00:49:40,852
Produser Seo.

641
00:49:42,854 --> 00:49:43,689
Ya?

642
00:49:46,108 --> 00:49:46,942
Sekarang…

643
00:49:49,569 --> 00:49:52,030
kau resmi tak punya pacar?

644
00:49:58,036 --> 00:49:59,830
Boleh kuanggap seperti itu?

645
00:50:03,291 --> 00:50:04,710
Ya, tentu.

646
00:50:10,132 --> 00:50:11,091
Mulai sekarang…

647
00:50:18,765 --> 00:50:20,475
boleh kulakukan yang aku mau?

648
00:53:39,507 --> 00:53:44,387
Terjemahan subtitle oleh Maharani Djenial

